SimplePHP Source

A bunch of PHP classes making everyday code easier and comfortable. Static functions for simple access of common uses.

Add the following lines to your code to use SimplePHP's functions:

// Define SimplePHP's absolute path and load init script
define ('PATH_SIMPLEPHP', YOUR_ABSOLUTE_PATH . 'to/SimplePHP/');
require_once (PATH_SIMPLEPHP . 'init.php');